title: Lisa Jackson-Left to Die
description:
In Left to Die, the Pinewood County Sheriff s Department is on the trail of a cold-blooded killer who acts as a savior to women stranded during terrible mountain snowstorms before stripping them of their dignity and leaving them to die, a victim of the elements. 
 But the killers latest victim managed to escape, leading some to believe there may now be an imposter on the loose.
